about.summary: A system for assigning and grading Jupyter notebooks

name: nbgrader
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.8.5" %}

package:
  name: nbgrader
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/n/nbgrader/nbgrader-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 22ea4a53cf77fccbe4aea10196782040a4d9f357730a463b0eb3db368311dea4

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script:
    - {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --no-build-isolation -vv
  entry_points:
    - nbgrader = nbgrader.apps.nbgraderapp:main

requirements:
  host:
    - hatch-jupyter-builder >=0.7
    - hatchling >=1.10.0
    - jupyterlab >=3.1,<4
    - pip
    - python >=3.8
  run:
    - alembic >=1.7
    - ipython >=8.10.0
    - ipywidgets >=7.6
    - jinja2 >=3
    - jsonschema >=3
    - jupyter_client <9
    - jupyter_server >=1.12,<2
    - jupyterlab >=3.1,<4
    - jupyterlab_server
    - nbclient >=0.6.1
    - nbconvert >=6
    - notebook >=6.4,<7
    - python >=3.8
    - python-dateutil >=2.8
    - rapidfuzz >=1.8
    - requests >=2.26
    - sqlalchemy >=1.4,<3
    - traitlets >5.0,<6

test:
  requires:
    - pip
    - m2-grep  # [win]
    - jupyterlab
  imports:
    - nbgrader
  commands:
    - pip check
    - nbgrader -h
    - jupyter lab --version
    - jupyter notebook --version
    - jupyter labextension list
    - jupyter server extension list
    - jupyter serverextension list
    - jupyter labextension list 1>labextensions 2>&1
    - jupyter server extension list 1>server_extensions 2>&1
    - jupyter serverextension list 1>serverextensions 2>&1
    {% for ext in ["assignment_list", "course_list", "formgrader", "validate_assignment"] %}
    - grep -iE "nbgrader.server_extensions.{{ ext }}.*OK" server_extensions
    - grep -iE "nbgrader.server_extensions.{{ ext }}.*enabled" server_extensions
    - grep -iE "nbgrader.server_extensions.{{ ext }}.*OK" serverextensions
    - grep -iE "nbgrader.server_extensions.{{ ext }}.*enabled" serverextensions
    {% endfor %}
    - grep -iE "nbgrader.*OK.*nbgrader" labextensions

about:
  home: https://github.com/jupyter/nbgrader
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file:
    - LICENSE
    - nbgrader/labextension/static/third-party-licenses.json
  summary: A system for assigning and grading Jupyter notebooks
  doc_url: https://nbgrader.readthedocs.io

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - blink1073
    - jhamrick
    - lgpage
    - ocefpaf
    - BertR
    - SylvainCorlay
    - bollwyvl
